(22, 76, 'Don’t know what to do with your kids for the coming school holidays?', 'camping-content-1', '', '<div class="float-left document menu2-cnt">\r\n<h4>Don’t know what to do with your kids for the coming school holidays?</h4>\r\n<p>Send them to one of our adventure camps for some fun and excitement!</p>\r\n<p>We offer adventure camps during the school holidays starting at the end of March</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Bidoup Nui Ba National Park</li>\r\n<li>Dalat</li>\r\n<li>Madagui</li>\r\n<li>North</li>\r\n<li>Seaside</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Info &amp; registration: info@asia-motions.com</p>\r\n<h4>Our vision</h4>\r\n<p>Our holiday camps are a great way to experience new activities, learn new skills, open one''s mind and make new friends in a safe environment.</p>\r\n<p>We will teach your kids how to maneuver in the forest, build and set up a campsite, cook and backpack in some of the country''s most beautiful places.</p>\r\n<p>They will return home with unforgettable memories!</p>\r\n<p><a href="index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=featured&amp;Itemid=118#contact_us_form">Contact us to get more details about our camps!</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="float-right document menu2-cnt"><img src="images/img1.jpg" border="0" alt="" />\r\n<div class="border-cnt">\r\n<p>A great learning experience for the young!</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Live with others &amp; adapt to new situations</li>\r\n<li>Select a campsite</li>\r\n<li>Pitch your tent &amp; build functional items</li>\r\n<li>Create wooden tools &amp; learn to use basic knots</li>\r\n<li>Track identifications, recognize plants &amp; animals</li>\r\n<li>Learn about hiking &amp; orienteering techniques</li>\r\n<li>Prepare and cook a meal by themselves</li>\r\n<li>Build &amp; prepare a fire site</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 0, 0, 15, '2014-05-21 03:21:05', 820, '', '2014-05-29 07:34:51', 820, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-05-21 03:21:05', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":""