(25, 79, 'Adventure Camp', 'adventure-camp', '', '<div class="widthgrid clearfix document">\r\n<p>This Adventure Camp is focusing on the connection between the kids and the nature, allowing them to spend lots of time outdoors.Big highlight is the Camping part in</p>\r\n<p>Bidoup where kids really have an enriching and unique experience: they face new situations everyday, meet new social challenges, have to solve problems and have to go out of their comfort zone. They learn self confidence and self control.</p>\r\n<p>During this 6-days multiactivities camp, kids will do many fun and exciting activities and will have a real blast.</p>\r\n<img src="images/img3.jpg" border="0" alt="" />\r\n<div class="box-cle">\r\n<h3>ADVENTURE HOLIDAY CAMP IN BIDOUP</h3>\r\n<p align="center">Departure Monday morning 8 am</p>\r\n<table width="100%" border="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td align="center"><strong>Day 1</strong></td>\r\n<td align="center"><strong>Day 2</strong></td>\r\n<td align="center">Day 3</td>\r\n<td align="center"><strong>Day 4</strong></td>\r\n<td align="center"><strong>Day 5</strong></td>\r\n<td align="center"><strong>Day 6</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Transfer by bus from HCM to Madagui</td>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>Rock climbing <br /> swimming pool <br /> games</p>\r\n<p>Transfer to Dalat</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>CANYONING</td>\r\n<td>- JUNGLE TREK UP MOUNT BIDOUP &amp; BIVOUAC</td>\r\n<td>- TREK BACK TO BIDOUP PARK</td>\r\n<td>- MOUNTAIN BIKING THROUGH THE PINE FOREST &amp; DOWN TO NHA TRANG (2-3H)</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>Lunch at Madagui</td>\r\n<td>Pic Nic lunch</td>\r\n<td>Pic Nic lunch</td>\r\n<td>Pic Nic lunch</td>\r\n<td>Lunch at the camp site</td>\r\n<td>Lunch</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>ZIPLINE TREK</td>\r\n<td>ACTIVITIES in <br /> Dalat forest</td>\r\n<td>Transfer to Bidoup <br /> National Park &amp; <br /> BUILDING OF THE <br /> CAMP SITE</td>\r\n<td>Bivouac near the <br /> summit</td>\r\n<td>ORIENTEERING <br /> GAMES - BIKING <br /> TRAINING</td>\r\n<td>