(65, 120, 'Education Content', 'education-content', '', '<p> </p>\r\n<p><span style="line-height: 1.3em;"><img src="images/IMG_1683 main pic 2.jpg" border="0" alt="" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" /></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="line-height: 1.3em;">Learning is more effective when it is an active rather than a passive process." - Kurt Lewin We aim to organize customized school trips with activity-based contents linked to your curriculum objectives and encourage students to develop their general awareness. We cover different subjects, working closely with teachers to make activities come alive and to bridge the gap between textbook theory and hands-on experience, adapted to the destination and to the students’ ages.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="line-height: 1.3em;"><img src="images/IMG_5587 main pic 1.jpg" border="0" alt="" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" /></span></p>\r\n<p>Examples of our pedagogical fields are: geography (study and observation of rivers &amp; forests, coffee &amp; cocoa plantation visits, etc.); physical education &amp; outdoor activities; history (visits of historic sites); sciences (observation &amp; practical experiments, educational trekking); eco explorer (impact of humans on the environment, recycling concept); handicrafts (kite or lantern making) and skill based workshops (orienteering, shelter building, etc.) Our school trips aim to stimulate the mind and the senses with each new experience being a chance for students to learn more about certain subjects, the world and their own potential. Contact us to get more details about our trips!</p>', '', 1, 0, 0, 14, '2014-05-28 11:11:41', 820, '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-05-28 11:11:41', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,